name: com.castsoftware.sqlanalyzer
title: SQL Analyzer
description: SQL Analyzer provides official support for PostgreSQL, MySQL, MariaDB, SQLite, DB2, Informix, Sybase ASE, Microsoft SQL Server and Teradata. Especially designed to analyze sql files, both DDL and DML, it is intended for determining transactions and assessing quality. ANSI SQL-92 and ANSI SQL-99 compliant.
